metadata.name: Millenium Falcon 1.60 km
metadata.description:
Millenium Falcon (Star Wars).

GPS Drawing, also known as GPS Art, is a method of drawing where an artist uses a Global Positioning System (GPS) device and follows a pre-planned route to create a large-scale picture or pattern. 

Distance: 1.16 km
Moving time: 13:36
Location: Kharkiv, Ukraine
Resolution: 1200x1200
